<TITLE> Death toll rises in US helicopter crash in Italy </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 ROME, Nov 9 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - A sixth US military person has died from his wounds after a US army Black Hawk helicopter crashed in northern Italy with 11 people on board, a hospital spokesman said on Friday. The helicopter, which according to media reports was on a training mission and had taken off from a US military base in Italy, crashed on Thursday in a grassy field near the city of Treviso. The cause of the crash has yet to be establish
